<subSubSection id="C3796513FFEAFFF6FC8BFD43FC7813FE" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BDC3698FFEAFFF6FC8BFD43FC7813FE" blockId="2.[869,1494,730,915]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FC8BFD43FC30129E" bold="true" box="[869,994,730,755]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<typeStatus id="54D8883AFFEAFFF6FC8BFD43FC4C129E" box="[869,926,730,755]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Type</typeStatus>
data:
</emphasis>
This species was described based on an undetermined number of specimens of both sexes collect‑ ed in the province of 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FBBDFC83FB68135E" box="[1107,1210,794,819]" country="Argentina" name="San Juan" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">San Juan</collectingRegion>
, northwestern 
<collectingCountry id="F3747608FFEAFFF6FA8FFC83FA00135E" box="[1377,1490,794,819]" name="Argentina" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. The 
<typeStatus id="54D8883AFFEAFFF6FC79FCA3FC1B133E" box="[919,969,826,851]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">type</typeStatus>
series was not found during the development of this research and it is apparently lost (
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFEAFFF6FABCFCC3FC7213FE" author="Roig-Alsina, A." pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="171 - 193" refId="ref4820" refString="Roig-Alsina, A. 2000. Claves para las especies argentinas de Centris (Hymenoptera, Apidae), con descripcion de nuevas especies y notas sobre distribucion. Revista del Museo Argentino de Ciencias Naturales, 2 (2): 171 - 193." type="journal article" year="2000">Roig‑Alsina, 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3796513FFEAFFF6FC8BFC23FB04157E" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BDC3698FFEAFFF6FC8BFC23FB04157E" blockId="2.[869,1494,954,1299]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FC8BFC23FC3E13BE" bold="true" box="[869,1004,954,979]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Comments:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFEAFFF6FC17FC23FB1613BE" author="Schrottky, C." box="[1017,1220,954,979]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="309 - 315" refId="ref4866" refString="Schrottky, C. 1902 a. Hymenopteres noveaux de l'Amerique Meridionale. Anales del Museo Nacional de Buenos Aires, 7: 309 - 315." type="journal article" year="1902">Schrottky (1902a)</bibRefCitation>
dedicated this species to the Argentinean zoologist and ornithologist Enrique Lynch Arribálzaga (1856‑1935) who funded with his countryman the botanist, zoologist and geologist Eduardo Ladislao Holmberg (1852‑1937) in 1878 “El Naturalista Argentino”, the first journal of Natural History of 
<collectingCountry id="F3747608FFEAFFF6FC6DFBE3FC2314FE" box="[899,1009,1146,1171]" name="Argentina" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFEAFFF6FC11FBE3FB1514FE" author="Lopez, H. L. &amp; Miquelarena, A. M. &amp; Gomez, J. P." box="[1023,1223,1146,1171]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="1 - 73" refId="ref4255" refString="Lopez, H. L.; Miquelarena, A. M. &amp; Gomez, J. P. 2008. Ictiologos de la Argentina Eduardo Ladislao Holmberg. ProBiota, FCN y M. UNLP Serie Tecnica y Didactica, 14 (1): 1 - 73." type="journal article" year="2008">
López 
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFEAFFF6FBA3FBE3FB5514FE" box="[1101,1159,1146,1171]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">et al.,</emphasis>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
). This species occurs exclusively in 
<collectingCountry id="F3747608FFEAFFF6FC01FB03FB8F14DE" box="[1007,1117,1178,1203]" name="Argentina" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Argentina</collectingCountry>
with distribution records in the provinces of 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FC15FB23FB4214BE" box="[1019,1168,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="Ciudad Autonoma de Buenos Aires" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Buenos Aires</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FB72FB23FAC714BE" box="[1180,1301,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="Catamarca" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Catamarca</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FACCFB23FAB814BE" box="[1314,1386,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="Chaco" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Chaco</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FA98FB23FA0114BE" box="[1398,1491,1210,1235]" country="Argentina" name="La Rioja" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">La Rioja</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FC8BFB43FC1D149E" box="[869,975,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Mendoza" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Mendoza</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FC35FB43FBE8149E" box="[987,1082,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="San Luis" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">San Luis</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FBABFB43FB75149E" box="[1093,1191,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Santa Fe" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Santa Fe</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FB5CFB43FA5D149E" box="[1202,1423,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Santiago del Estero" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Santiago del Estero</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FA77FB43FA00149E" box="[1433,1490,1242,1267]" country="Argentina" name="Salta" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Salta</collectingRegion>
, and 
<collectingRegion id="49A7F87AFFEAFFF6FC7BFB63FC2E157E" box="[917,1020,1274,1299]" country="Argentina" name="Tucuman" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Tucumán</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFEAFFF6FBE9FB63FB1F157E" author="Roig-Alsina, A." box="[1031,1229,1274,1299]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" pagination="171 - 193" refId="ref4820" refString="Roig-Alsina, A. 2000. Claves para las especies argentinas de Centris (Hymenoptera, Apidae), con descripcion de nuevas especies y notas sobre distribucion. Revista del Museo Argentino de Ciencias Naturales, 2 (2): 171 - 193." type="journal article" year="2000">Roig‑Alsina, 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
